data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This fully updated 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home is located in the desirable Southern Hills neighborhood and boasts a charming living room with a cast iron fireplace. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring beautiful granite countertops and an open layout that flows seamlessly into the dining room. Plus, there's a separate oversized laundry room for your convenience. Step outside and you'll find a fully fenced backyard with a completed shed, perfect for storing all your outdoor tools and equipment. This home is move-in ready and waiting for you to make it your own. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to live in one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in town.
